&lt;li>Mix all ingredients, oil first&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Roll out&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Cook&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Banana Bread (Grandma Lonergan's)</title><link>https://mowery.dev/recipes/banana_bread_matt/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mowery.dev/recipes/banana_bread_matt/</guid><description>&lt;p>See original at &lt;a href="https://matt9j.net/recipes/banana-bread">matt9j.net/recipes/banana-bread&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>True origins unknown, but refined over many generations, this recipe
makes a delicious soft banana bread. For maximum enjoyment be sure to
not over-cook it, avoid over-mixing once you&amp;rsquo;ve combined the dry and
wet ingredients, and consider adding some dark chocolate chips or
favorite chopped nuts!&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="0-prework">0: Prework:&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Preheat oven to 325&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Lightly grease 9x5 loaf pan&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="1-in-a-large-bowl-mix">1: In a large bowl mix:&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>2 cups flour&lt;/li>
&lt;li>1 tsp baking soda&lt;/li>
&lt;li>½ tsp baking powder&lt;/li>
&lt;li>½ tsp salt&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="2-in-a-separate-bowl-mix">2: In a separate bowl mix:&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>1 ½ cup mashed overripe bananas (3-4)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>¾ cup sugar&lt;/li>
&lt;li>¾ cup vegetable oil&lt;/li>
&lt;li>2 eggs&lt;/li>
&lt;li>2 T vanilla (that is not a typo&amp;hellip; two tablespoons is correct)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="3-put-it-all-together">3: Put it all together:&lt;/h2>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Stir banana mixture into flour mixture; stir just to moisten.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Pour batter into prepared loaf pan.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Bake in preheated oven for 60-70 minutes, until a toothpick
inserted into center of the loaf comes out clean.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Let bread cool in pan for 10 minutes&amp;hellip;&lt;/li>
&lt;li>And then turn out onto a wire rack to finish cooling on its own!&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>Banana Bread (Laura)</title><link>https://mowery.dev/recipes/banana_bread_laura/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mowery.dev/recipes/banana_bread_laura/</guid><description>&lt;script type="application/ld+json">
